<p>[Page 23]</p>
<p>Monday 13.5.18&nbsp; Reconnoitring- had a game of cards with the Yanks. Wrote Doff.</p>
<p>Tuesday 14.5.18&nbsp; &quot;D&quot; Coy detached working &quot;C&quot; Coy&nbsp; concert &amp; Supper very pleasant Evening.</p>
<p>Wednesday 15.5.18&nbsp; Saw Martin &amp; Paton at Heilly- Had game of bridge.</p>
<p>Thursday 16.5 18&nbsp; Went to Bde HQrs&nbsp; letter from Bas, reconnoitring- D. Coy returned</p>
<p>Friday 17.5.18. Off color with touch of malaria- Officers reconnoitring</p>
<p>Saturday 18.5.18&nbsp; To Bde- Paton doing stunt tomorrow at Ville Sur Ancre [Ville-sur-Ancre]</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
